    "spell_type": "spell",
    "subtype": "spell",
    "text": "You summon a phantasmal minion. The minion is roughly the shape of a humanoid. You can choose to have it be invisible or have an ephemeral appearance, but it's obviously a magical effect, not a real creature.",
